headline: Trump, Senate Leaders Work Overtime to Secure Votes for Tax Bill
summary: (Bloomberg) -- Donald Trump and Senate Republican leaders worked Saturday to persuade reluctant holdouts to back the president’s multi-trillion dollar tax and spending bill ahead of a pivotal vote.
